					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Cute and anomalous, yay, I love it!<br /> However, the article mentions SCP-2454-1 instances in its special containment procedures, but SCP-2454-1 instances are not mentioned in the description (or at least not by name). I'm guessing that SCP-2454-1 instances are the adult states of SCP-2454 but that is never mentioned.</p> 
				 	]]>
