						 <p>Oh no, no no. You got me once with Python Pythons, you don't get to get me again.</p> <p>You go a bit too far in this one with the cuteness factor, giving these creatures so many minor, adorable features like the fire breathing, and the electricity, and the heightened intelligence only used for mimicry and being friggin' adorable. Nope!</p> <p>Sorry Xilas. Novote.</p> 
